S.FORM: Raúl Castro I 1931 a miheca saka 6 folad saka 3 a romi'ad masofoc ci Raúl Castro, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Cuba anini i ci Raúl Castro, patirengan a romi'ad i 2011 a miheca saka 4 folad saka 19 a romi'ad.
